<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
   <div rend="parallel">
     <p xml:id="Aink211-kilavi"> talaimaka ṉāṟṟāmai kaṇṭu kaiyuṟai yeṟṟa tōḻi talaimakaṭ ṭaḻai yēṟka vēṇṭik kūṟiyatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante who received the gift, witnessing the hero’s inability to bear [it otherwise], said to the heroine, urging [her] to accept the foliage.   </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink211">
<l>neyyoṭu mayakkiya vuḻuntu nūṟ ṟaṉṉa</l>
<l>vayalaiyañ cilampiṉ ṟalaiyatu</l>
<l>ceyalaiyam pakaittaḻai vāṭu maṉṉāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Mother! </l>
<l>The contrasting foliage of the Aśoka tree [gathered]</l>
<l rend="indent">from the peak of the mountain slope with purslane </l>
<l rend="indent">which are like threads of black gram mixed with ghee, </l>
<l>will wither away. </l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
